Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.81,0:00:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.92,0:00:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.13,0:00:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.93,0:00:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.21,0:01:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.57,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有人在破壞OZ的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和大家見面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七話\N[導致流血的劇本]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是新愛德華基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機也到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總共15部，數目很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經把OZ的所有高層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚集在新愛德華基地這假情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廣泛流傳開去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我和妳會出席是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己也是魚餌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備已100%完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不須再增加人手了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯在奈羅比嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點浪費了他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派駐奈羅比基地的OZ士兵很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡會變成激戰區吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.28,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就能毫不猶疑地獻身給歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新愛德華，OZ會齊集那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦那傢伙又失蹤了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，但他說會再回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙總是自以為是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來他被解雇也無話可說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，解雇他很可惜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來後我要好好教訓他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，你究竟想做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然獨自去了別墅遊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也還是小孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在我們這班污糟鬼之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也很累吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺打算留下我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自進行某項作戰行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會?真的?隊長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺擔心我們的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺\N豈不是有危險嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能白費\N卡特爾少爺的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事前我和商量一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊金山市史丹利酒店嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想訂房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個小孩沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們又見面了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地看來一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會自己行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是，但互相幫助會更順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會更順利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲啊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貨艙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.44,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，你也快點運進來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的工作我絕對不想出錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶而一起工作無所謂吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙，還記著我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會是一場激烈的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次任務的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是消滅OZ的絕佳機會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和以往不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次要收拾OZ這組織的首腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我就能回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球圈統一聯合\N新愛德華基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以最高司令官洛賓達元帥為首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,統領宇宙軍的賽普提姆將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球軍的班迪將軍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合最高層的人齊集召開會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，SMS(特務部隊)的特列斯上級特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,副官蕾蒂‧安二級特校也會出席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯暗中向全世界散播假消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這會議不是聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.84,0:07:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是OZ的首腦齊集召開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史會怎樣推展呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會照特列斯大人你的決定推展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看聯合的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是否要糾正它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈羅比基地要求和本編隊聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴他們這是演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會在蒙百沙上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行空中模擬戰   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，這次戰鬥會留下疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信傑克斯你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你命令說這攻擊是必需的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就會戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合和OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使換過來了，世界也不會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，為何要戰鬥? 傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對世界各國的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的抑制行動畢竟太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我們現在需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非威嚇世界的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軍備擴張，新武器開發方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經不須再耗費努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是聯合要行的正確之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換言之，是裁軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裁軍只是開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為最終一定要完全解除軍備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯   班迪將軍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我們曾經流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了實現統一的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那目的不知不覺地變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經要結束流血的時代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能結束就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，最近的一連串事件又如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用只有在宇宙才能煉製的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.55,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈合金的機動戰士的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球現在被那壓倒性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,置於危機之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實際戰鬥的SMS的何看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為那是\N殖民衛星的破壞活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合需要一名演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我飾演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出聯合真正心意的角色吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你們明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星不信任我們是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了消除那種不信任感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該馬上和他們開始對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.96,0:10:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類的新歷史要由對話開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不只是和衛星的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為也要和全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始相同的對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那些機動戰士的問題…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果知道我們的和平意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的破壞活動\N也就會失去意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談判後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不見的路\N也會在我們面前出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史果然向錯的方向推展嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要待最後的演員齊集後才開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為時代\N要朝著和平談判前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帥!是敵襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這基地受到攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這防線很嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十倍以上\N遠超過想像中的數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日不可退縮啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進攻須要太多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有突擊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，演員齊集了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也開幕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令開始[黎明行動]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，全體開始降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯絡駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴他們我們想和衛星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛賓達元帥!\N敵人已經展開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣做時，這裡的損毀會…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.17,0:13:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帥，現在先去避難較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也還想和衛星進行和平談判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帥你就不能在這戰鬥裡喪命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的諷刺我當聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確不想白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了實現和平談判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼請你使用\N我們的高速穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.79,0:13:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它能緊急出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.33,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你會想得\N這麼周詳和方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帥，我也是聯合的一份子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，那麼拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，我來帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機在B12發射場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賽普提姆將軍，請來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機不是在那邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以防萬一，分散穿梭機是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我專用的穿梭機在F7機發射場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能載那麼多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是SMS的最新機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能出擊的機動戰士全部出擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人只是兩部機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令!\N菲亞柏基地有緊急通訊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是叛變!\N部份士兵正發起叛變!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界各地的基地正發生叛變!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹長!不行!如果不投降…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂講!你也是叛徒嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SMS的小鬼有何作為!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.18,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這基地已經被占領，投降吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒給我住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就讓你嚐嚐革命的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妄想!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別衝動!諾茵特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建設是非常好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，為了建立那基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這未免流了太多血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，停止無益的反抗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想盡量多招攬些同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的時代已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的統一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要由我們OZ親手創立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和新秩序一起建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也講得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次政變是準備周詳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的士兵隱藏SMS的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派駐各地的聯合軍基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那也是\N聯合軍事組織的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.48,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的首腦受到毀滅性的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞洲、歐洲、非洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的各個基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被叛軍佔領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛賓達元帥現在在哪裡!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!查不到他的所在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟發生甚麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!一窩蜂湧出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛彈!?自己人也攻擊嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人密集在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日不能警告你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我比較不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的新型機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們攻擊聯合啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩部機體和我們一模一樣吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他們也是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰都好，阻礙的就要排除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩部機體好相似啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?為何不快點出發?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛賓達元帥\N他們的穿梭機先出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們隨後出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那部穿梭機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是不幸的巧合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為這是和平的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元…元師!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別衝動啊，年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛賓達元帥…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的飛彈招呼，多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次讓我招呼你啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意義的戰鬥你們還打不夠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們完全中了OZ的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開聯合的宣傳線路看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們把聯合的和平支持者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是衛星的宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們今日討論和衛星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堪稱中心人物的洛賓達元帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不在人世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被衛星派來侵略的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士殺死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是殘暴的侵略行為!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會向衛星屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定要戰鬥到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，賽普提姆將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，你的演出結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的演技好逼真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.97,0:21:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你離場有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不可以讓你\N防礙特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.05,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二幕開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切全是OZ的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.83,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被玩弄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在特列斯‧克修里那達的股掌之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會的…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.57,0:21:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.84,0:22:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣也好，我會和OZ戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使只有一個人也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.58,0:22:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.30,0:22:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.30,0:22:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.30,0:22:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.30,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.80,0:22:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.30,0:23:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.80,0:23:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.30,0:23:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.80,0:23:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯掌握了歷史的主導權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被OZ玩弄了的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.50,0:23:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和賽普提姆一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.94,0:23:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為被蕾蒂‧安陷害的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.81,0:23:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛、迪歐、卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.98,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命阻止新愛德華基地的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.14,0:23:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而五飛和特洛瓦迫近特列斯
